snippet.title: [HINDI] realme BGIS 2025 | SEMI FINALS - WEEK 01 | Day 4
snippet.description:
Dive into the heart of the battleground with realme BGIS 2025 SEMI FINALS Week 01! Witness 32 teams clash in a relentless pursuit of glory, but the first strongest 08 will advance to the Grand LAN Finals. Get ready for non-stop action, breathtaking battles, and strategic gameplay that will keep you on the edge of your seat. Each match is a testament to skill, strategy, and survival — who will dominate, and who will bow out? Don’t miss a moment of this epic showdown. Tune in, cheer on your favourite teams, and see who makes the mark to move one step closer to the ultimate victory in realme BGIS 2025!

#BGMI #BGISxrealme #BGIS2025 #MAKEYOURMARK #KRAFTONINDIAESPORTS #KIE #realmeBGIS2025

snippet.title: Bhide ने खींचा Abdul के साथ Jetha का पैर | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah| Jetha-Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

The men finally clean the premises and are relieved. The effects of strenuous work are showing and Jethalal feels tired. Meanwhile, Popatlal thanks the ladies for making them clean their respective houses. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1523
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Jetha Aur Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTAUo34hpXVbh1keqAyhuhj

Bhide ने खींचा Abdul के साथ Jetha का पैर | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah| Jetha-Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk

Aas Paas is a story of love, sacrifice, and the struggles within the relationships we often take for granted.
Arshia, a strong-willed young woman, is determined to reunite her broken family after her father abandons them. Meanwhile, Dr. Saham, a dedicated professional carrying his own burdens,

Episode 4361: Gudi Padwa In Gokuldham
--------------------------------------------------------
On the occasion of Gudi Padwa, the Bhides decide to make various jackfruit delicacies, bringing excitement to Gokuldham Colony as everyone prepares to celebrate the special day.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4361 | 2 Apr 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Karate Kid: Legends unites the iconic martial arts masters of one of the most beloved film franchises of all time to tell a completely new story full of action and heart. When kung fu prodigy Li Fong (Ben Wang) relocates to New York City with his mother to attend a prestigious new school, he finds solace in a new friendship with a classmate and her father. But his newfound peace is short-lived after he attracts unwanted attention from a formidable local karate champion. Driven by a desire to defend himself, Li embarks on a journey to enter the ultimate karate competition. Guided by the wisdom of his kung fu teacher, Mr. Han (Jackie Chan), and the legendary Karate Kid, Daniel LaRusso (Ralph Macchio), Li merges their unique styles to prepare for an epic martial arts showdown. 

Directed by: Jonathan Entwistle   
 
Written by: Rob Lieber    

Produced by: Karen Rosenfelt
          
Executive Producers:
Jenny Hinkey
Ralph Macchio

snippet.title: Sikandar Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Sikandar Salman Khan Comeback Movie Directed by AR Murugadoss with Rashmika Mandanna is totally wasted opportunity with Old Mass & Funny Emotions combined with Slow Salman Khan Action & Bigger than life poor presentation.

Sikandar Full Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma with Positives & Negatives would be shared in this Video. Bollywood Biggest Fanbase Star Salman Khan actually tried his best or Another chance would be needed for Much Awaited Comeback? Find Clear answer inside!

Sikandar is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film directed by A. R. Murugadoss and produced by Sajid Nadiadwala. The film stars Salman Khan in the titular role, alongside Rashmika Mandanna, Sathyaraj, Kajal Aggarwal, Sharman Joshi, Prateik Babbar, Kishore, Jatin Sarna and Sanjay Kapoor. In the film, Sanjay "Sikandar" Rajkot, the king of Rajkot, becomes a target for Minister Rakesh Pradhan after killing his son. When his wife’s donated organs save three lives, Rakesh seeks revenge, forcing Sanjay to protect them.

The film was officially announced in April 2024. Principal photography commenced the following June in Mumbai and wrapped by March 2025. The film has songs composed by Pritam, background score composed by Santhosh Narayanan, cinematography handled by Tirru and editing by Vivek Harshan. With an estimated production budget of ₹200 crore, it is one of the most expensive Indian films of all time.

Sikandar was theatrically released worldwide on 30 March 2025, in standard and IMAX formats, coinciding with Eid al-Fitr.

Sikandar Full Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma with Positives & Negatives would be shared in this Video. Bollywood Biggest Fanbase Star Salman Khan actually tried his best or Another chance would be needed for Much Awaited Comeback? Find Clear answer inside!

Sikandar is a 2025 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film directed by A. R. Murugadoss and produced by Sajid Nadiadwala. The film stars Salman Khan in the titular role, alongside Rashmika Mandanna, Sathyaraj, Kajal Aggarwal, Sharman Joshi, Prateik Babbar, Kishore, Jatin Sarna and Sanjay Kapoor. In the film, Sanjay "Sikandar" Rajkot, the king of Rajkot, becomes a target for Minister Rakesh Pradhan after killing his son. When his wife’s donated organs save three lives, Rakesh seeks revenge, forcing Sanjay to protect them.

The film was officially announced in April 2024. Principal photography commenced the following June in Mumbai and wrapped by March 2025. The film has songs composed by Pritam, background score composed by Santhosh Narayanan, cinematography handled by Tirru and editing by Vivek Harshan. With an estimated production budget of ₹200 crore, it is one of the most expensive Indian films of all time.

Sikandar was theatrically released worldwide on 30 March 2025, in standard and IMAX formats, coinciding with Eid al-Fitr.

आज के The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 352nd Episode में हमारे साथ हैं Palga Rinpoche, एक Buddhist Monk, जिन्होंने Buddhism, Karma, Forgiveness और Spiritual Growth के विषय में गहरी समझ साझा की। यह Episode न केवल Self-Reflection और Acceptance की बात करता है, बल्कि Life Transformation और Inner Peace की ओर भी मार्गदर्शन देता है।

Palga Rinpoche के साथ इस बातचीत में हम जानेंगे Karma, Anger और Forgiveness का महत्व, और Meditation की शक्ति के बारे में। साथ ही यह भी समझेंगे कि कैसे Spiritual Practices हमारी मुश्किलों को एक अवसर में बदल सकती हैं।

यह Hindi Podcast उन सभी के लिए एक अनमोल अनुभव है जो Self-Healing और Inner Growth की राह पर चलना चाहते हैं।

snippet.title: BGIS 8 SOLO KILLS | JONATHAN IS BACK | BGMI!
snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4360 | 1 Apr 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4360: Kathal Season
--------------------------------------------------------
The colony is filled with joy when Bhide shares jackfruit with everyone after receiving a large supply from his uncle’s farm. But the women face a challenge figuring out how to prepare it.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4360 | 1 Apr 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090476001

snippet.title: The Bhootnii (Official Trailer) | Sanjay D, Mouni R, Sunny S, Palak T, Nick | Sidhaant S | Deepak M
snippet.description:
Get ready for a spooky, hilarious, and mind-bending ride with The Bhootnii 👻🎬 This horror-comedy-sci-fi adventure brings together the best of chills and laughs, starring Sanjay Dutt as the fearless Ghostbuster Baba, who must face the ultimate paranormal challenge: Mouni Roy as a powerful and mysterious ghost.

Joining this epic journey are Sunny Singh, Palak Tiwari, Aasif Khan and Beyounick, bringing their comedic chops and unforgettable performances to the screen. With Baba and his team on a mission to stop the ghostly forces, prepare for a rollercoaster of supernatural thrills and gut-busting moments.

Will Baba and his quirky team defeat Bhootnii or will the ghost take over?

The Bhootnii hits theaters on 18th April 2025! 
Don’t miss this epic horror-comedy-sci-fi adventure! 🎬 

Credits : 
⭐ cast : Sanjay Dutt, Mouni Roy, Sunny Singh, Palak, Asif Khan, BeYounik & Others
Written & Directed by : Sidhaant Sachdev
Produced by : Deepak Mukut & Sanjay Dutt
Co-Produced by : Hunar Mukut & Maanayata Dutt
Associate Producer : Johari Tailor
DOP : Santosh Thundiyil ISC
Editor : Bunty Nagi

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Real Madrid 4-4 Real Sociedad | Copa del Rey 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid booked their place in the final of the Copa del Rey and on 26 April they will battle it out against Barcelona or Atlético at La Cartuja stadium (Seville) for the trophy. The match was decided in extra-time, following a nail-biting end to the game. Barrenetxea gave Real Sociedad the lead after 16 minutes and Endrick made it 1-1 in the 30th minute after an exquisite assist from Vini Jr. with the outside of his right foot. In the second half, two Alaba own goals made it 1-3 in the 80th minute, but from 82‘ to 86’ Madrid rampaged and Bellingham, after another precise assist from Vini Jr, and Tchouameni brought the score to 3-3. In the 93rd minute, Oyarzabal took the game into extra-time, where the Whites sealed their semi-final berth in the 115th minute when Rüdiger headed home Güler's corner.
#LaCopaMola

es.title: RESUMEN | Real Madrid 4-4 Real Sociedad | Copa del Rey 2024/25
es.description:
El Real Madrid ya está en la final de la Copa del Rey y el 26 de abril luchará por el título frente al Barcelona o el Atlético en el estadio La Cartuja (Sevilla). El pase se decidió en la prórroga, a la que llegó el partido tras un final de infarto. Barrenetxea adelantó a la Real Sociedad a los 16 minutos y Endrick logró el 1-1 en el 30’ tras una excepcional asistencia de Vini Jr. con el exterior del pie derecho. En la segunda mitad, un autogol de Alaba y un tanto de Oyarzabal pusieron un 1-3 en el minuto 80, pero del 82’ al 86’ el Madrid fue un vendaval y Bellingham, tras otra precisa asistencia de Vini Jr., y Tchouameni hicieron el 3-3. Oyarzabal, en el minuto 93, llevó el partido a la prórroga, en la que nuestro equipo sentenció la semifinal en el minuto 115 al cabecear Rüdiger un córner sacado por Güler.
#LaCopaMola

snippet.title: The New Air India Airbus A350 Business Class from London to Delhi | Worst to Best ✈️🇮🇳
snippet.description:
The New Air India ! London to New Delhi on Air India’s New Airbus A350 Business Class #techtraveleat #travel #airindia 

I'm heading home after completing the KL2UK journey! I flew from London to New Delhi with Air India and then continued to Coimbatore. This time, I had the pleasure of flying on Air India's brand-new Airbus A350. After many past disappointments with air travel, Air India truly exceeded my expectations! Check out the video for all the details.

KL2UK യാത്ര പൂർത്തിയാക്കിയ ശേഷം ഞാൻ നാട്ടിലേക്ക് മടങ്ങുകയാണ്. London ൽ നിന്നും Air India വിമാനത്തിൽ New Delhi യിലേക്കും, ശേഷം അവിടെനിന്ന് കോയമ്പത്തൂരിലേക്കുമായിരുന്നു എന്റെ യാത്ര. Air India യുടെ പുതുപുത്തൻ Airbus A350 വിമാനത്തിലാണ് ഞാൻ യാത്ര ചെയ്തത്. മുൻപ് യാത്ര ചെയ്തപ്പോൾ പലതവണ മോശം അനുഭവങ്ങളായിരുന്നുവെങ്കിലും ഇത്തവണ Air India എന്നെ ഞെട്ടിച്ചുകളഞ്ഞു! കൂടുതൽ വിശേഷങ്ങൾ വീഡിയോയിൽ കാണാം.

00:00 Intro
02:13 Farewell to friends
03:25 Queens Terminal, LHR
05:29 Air India’s A350
06:31 Air India A350 Business Class
14:01 Take Off
18:38 Entertainment
19:58 Inflight Breakfast
21:17 Toilet
21:49 Inflight Cocktails
24:45 Inflight Lunch
27:22 Landing at Delhi Airport
29:10 Indira Gandhi International Airport, New Delhi
30:56 Stay at Delhi Airport
32:24 Conclusion

snippet.title: Unleash Your Inner Clash
snippet.description:
It is time to Unleash Your Inner Clash.

WWE Superstars arrive in Clash. Get ready.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

© 2025 Supercell Oy. CLASH OF CLANS is a trademark of Supercell Oy. All Rights Reserved. Game includes in app purchases and random rewards.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: Veera Dheera Sooran Roast | Plip Plip
snippet.description:
Veera Dheera Sooran, directed by Arun Kumar, is an action thriller starring Vedan and Dushara Vijayan in lead roles. This film is actually a sequel to the cult classic Veera Dheera Sooran - Part 1. Being tasked with following up such a beloved film must have been a stressful challenge for Arun Kumar, and it shows—resulting in a barely passable attempt that doesn't quite live up to the original's charm.

snippet.title: Durga Chalisa | श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Sohini Mishra | Durga Bhajan | Durga Mata Bhajan | Navratri
snippet.description:
Durga Chalisa | श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Sohini Mishra | Durga Bhajan | Durga Mata Bhajan | Navratri

🙏 श्री दुर्गा चालीसा 🙏 – A powerful and divine Durga Chalisa sung by Sohini Mishra, dedicated to Maa Durga, the supreme goddess of strength, protection, and wisdom. Chanting Durga Chalisa with devotion removes obstacles, fears, and negativity from life and brings prosperity, peace, and blessings.

🌺 Let this soulful rendition fill your heart with faith and devotion as you seek the grace of Maa Durga. 🌺

Title :- Shree Durga Chalisa
Singer :- Sohini Mishra 
Music Director :- Sohini Mishra
Lyrics :- Traditional 
Video :- Mindpro Agency

🌸 Chant "Jai Mata Di" and invoke the blessings of Maa Durga! 🌸

अपने दिन को सकारात्मक ऊर्जा से भरने के लिए सब्सक्राइब कीजिये और अपने मित्र परिवार के साथ शेर कीजिये| 
🔔 SUBSCRIBE NOW: 
https://www.youtube.com/@ShemarooBhakti

श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Shri Durga Chalisa
॥ दोहा ॥
नमो नमो दुर्गे सुख करनी।
Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni.

नमो नमो अम्बे दुःख हरनी॥
Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni.

॥ चौपाई ॥
निरंकार है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
Nirankar Hai Jyoti Tumhari.

तिहूं लोक फैली उजियारी॥
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari.

शशि ललाट मुख महाविशाला।
Shashi Lalat Mukh Mahavishala.

नेत्र लाल भृकुटि विकराला॥
Netra Lal Bhrikuti Vikarala.

रूप मातु को अधिक सुहावे।
Roop Matu Ko Adhik Suhave.

दरश करत जन अति सुख पावे॥
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Pave.

तुम संसार शक्ति लै कीना।
Tum Sansar Shakti Lai Keena.

पालन हेतु अन्न धन दीना॥
Palan Hetu Ann Dhan Deena.

अन्नपूर्णा हुई जग पाला।
Annapurna Hui Jag Pala.

तुम ही आदि सुन्दरी बाला॥
Tum Hi Aadi Sundari Bala.

प्रलयकाल सब नाशन हारी।
Pralay Kaal Sab Nashan Haari.

तुम गौरी शिवशंकर प्यारी॥
Tum Gauri Shivshankar Pyari.

शिव योगी तुम्हरे गुण गावें।
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaven.

ब्रह्मा विष्णु तुम्हे नित ध्यावें॥
Brahma Vishnu Tumhe Nit Dhyaven.

रूप सरस्वती को तुम धारा।
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara.

दे सुबुद्धि ऋषि मुनिन उबारा॥
De Subuddhi Rishi Munin Ubara.

धरयो रूप नरसिंह को अम्बा।
Dharyo Roop Narsingh Ko Amba.

परगट भई फाड़कर खम्बा॥
Pargat Bhayi Fadkar Khamba.

रक्षा करि प्रह्लाद बचायो।
Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo.

हिरण्याक्ष को स्वर्ग पठायो॥
Hiranyaksha Ko Swarg Pathayo.

लक्ष्मी रूप धरो जग माहीं।
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahi.

श्री नारायण अंग समाहीं॥
Shri Narayan Ang Samahi.

क्षीरसिन्धु में करत विलासा।
Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilasa.

दयासिन्धु दीजै मन आसा॥
Dayasindhu Deejai Man Aasa.

हिंगलाज में तुम्हीं भवानी।
Hinglaj Mein Tumhi Bhavani.

महिमा अमित न जात बखानी॥
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani.

मातंगी अरु धूमावती माता।
Matangi Aru Dhumavati Mata.

भुवनेश्वरी बगलामुखि माता॥
Bhuvaneshwari Baglamukhi Mata.

श्री भैरव तारा जग तारी।
Shri Bhairav Tara Jag Tari.

छिन्न भाल भव दुःख निवारी॥
Chhinn Bhal Bhav Dukh Nivari.

केहरि वाहन सोह भवानी।
Kehr Vahan Soh Bhavani.

लांगुर वीर चलत अगवानी॥
Langur Veer Chalat Agvani.

कर में खप्पर खड्ग विराजै।
Kar Mein Khappar Khadg Virajai.

जाको देख काल डर भाजै॥
Jako Dekh Kaal Dar Bhajai.

सोहै अस्त्र और त्रिशूला।
Sohai Astra Aur Trishula.

जाते उठत शत्रु हिय शूला॥
Jaate Uthat Shatru Hiy Shula.

नागार्जुन को दिया सहाई।
Nagarjun Ko Diya Sahayai.

ताहि जीति बने जगत गुराई॥
Tahi Jeet Bane Jagat Gurai.

शुम्भ निशुम्भ दानव तुम मारे।
Shumbh Nishumbh Danav Tum Maare.

रक्तबीज शंखन संहारे॥
Raktabeej Shankhan Sanhare.

महिषासुर नृप अति अभिमानी।
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani.

जेहि अघ भार मही अकुलानी॥
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulani.

रूप कराल कालिका धारा।
Roop Karal Kalika Dhara.

सेन सहित तुम तिहि संहारा॥
Sen Sahit Tum Tihi Sanhara.

परी गाढ़ संतन पर जब जब।
Pari Gaadh Santan Par Jab Jab.

भई सहाय मातु तुम तब तब॥
Bhayi Sahay Matu Tum Tab Tab.

अमरपुरी अरु बासव लोका।
Amarpuri Aru Basav Loka.

तब महिमा सब रहें अशोका॥
Tab Mahima Sab Rahen Ashoka.

ज्वाला में है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari.

तुमको सदा पूजें नरनारी॥
Tumko Sada Poojen Narnari.

प्रेम भक्ति से जो यश गावे।
Prem Bhakti Se Jo Yash Gave.

दुःख दारिद्र निकट नहिं आवे॥
Dukh Daridr Nikat Nahi Aave.

ध्यावे तुम्हें जो नर मन लाई।
Dhyave Tumhe Jo Nar Man Laai.

जनम मरन ताकौ छुटि जाई॥
Janam Maran Tako Chhuti Jaai.

जोगी सुर मुनि कहत पुकारी।
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukari.

योग न हो बिन शक्ति तुम्हारी॥
Yog Na Ho Bin Shakti Tumhari.

॥ दोहा ॥
शंकर आचारज तप कीनो।
Shankar Aacharya Tap Kino.

काम अरु क्रोध जीति सब लीनो॥
Kaam Aru Krodh Jeet Sab Leeno.

निशिदिन ध्यान धरो शंकर को।
Nishidin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko.

काहु काल नहिं सुमिरो तुमको॥
Kahu Kaal Nahi Sumiro Tumko.

शक्ति रूप का मरम न पायो।
Shakti Roop Ka Maram Na Payo.

शक्ति गई तब मन पछितायो॥
Shakti Gayi Tab Man Pachhitayo.

॥ समापन ॥
शरणागत हुई कीर्ति बखानी।
Sharanagat Hui Kirti Bakhani.

जय जय जय जगदम्ब भवानी॥
Jai Jai Jai Jagdamba Bhavani.

🌸 जय माता दी! 🌸
Jai Mata Di!

en.description:
Durga Chalisa | श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Sohini Mishra | Durga Bhajan | Durga Mata Bhajan | Navratri

🙏 श्री दुर्गा चालीसा 🙏 – A powerful and divine Durga Chalisa sung by Sohini Mishra, dedicated to Maa Durga, the supreme goddess of strength, protection, and wisdom. Chanting Durga Chalisa with devotion removes obstacles, fears, and negativity from life and brings prosperity, peace, and blessings.

🌺 Let this soulful rendition fill your heart with faith and devotion as you seek the grace of Maa Durga. 🌺

Title :- Shree Durga Chalisa
Singer :- Sohini Mishra 
Music Director :- Sohini Mishra
Lyrics :- Traditional 
Video :- Mindpro Agency

🌸 Chant "Jai Mata Di" and invoke the blessings of Maa Durga! 🌸

अपने दिन को सकारात्मक ऊर्जा से भरने के लिए सब्सक्राइब कीजिये और अपने मित्र परिवार के साथ शेर कीजिये| 
🔔 SUBSCRIBE NOW: 
https://www.youtube.com/@ShemarooBhakti

श्री दुर्गा चालीसा | Shri Durga Chalisa
॥ दोहा ॥
नमो नमो दुर्गे सुख करनी।
Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni.

नमो नमो अम्बे दुःख हरनी॥
Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni.

॥ चौपाई ॥
निरंकार है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
Nirankar Hai Jyoti Tumhari.

तिहूं लोक फैली उजियारी॥
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari.

शशि ललाट मुख महाविशाला।
Shashi Lalat Mukh Mahavishala.

नेत्र लाल भृकुटि विकराला॥
Netra Lal Bhrikuti Vikarala.

रूप मातु को अधिक सुहावे।
Roop Matu Ko Adhik Suhave.

दरश करत जन अति सुख पावे॥
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Pave.

तुम संसार शक्ति लै कीना।
Tum Sansar Shakti Lai Keena.

पालन हेतु अन्न धन दीना॥
Palan Hetu Ann Dhan Deena.

अन्नपूर्णा हुई जग पाला।
Annapurna Hui Jag Pala.

तुम ही आदि सुन्दरी बाला॥
Tum Hi Aadi Sundari Bala.

प्रलयकाल सब नाशन हारी।
Pralay Kaal Sab Nashan Haari.

तुम गौरी शिवशंकर प्यारी॥
Tum Gauri Shivshankar Pyari.

शिव योगी तुम्हरे गुण गावें।
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaven.

ब्रह्मा विष्णु तुम्हे नित ध्यावें॥
Brahma Vishnu Tumhe Nit Dhyaven.

रूप सरस्वती को तुम धारा।
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara.

दे सुबुद्धि ऋषि मुनिन उबारा॥
De Subuddhi Rishi Munin Ubara.

धरयो रूप नरसिंह को अम्बा।
Dharyo Roop Narsingh Ko Amba.

परगट भई फाड़कर खम्बा॥
Pargat Bhayi Fadkar Khamba.

रक्षा करि प्रह्लाद बचायो।
Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo.

हिरण्याक्ष को स्वर्ग पठायो॥
Hiranyaksha Ko Swarg Pathayo.

लक्ष्मी रूप धरो जग माहीं।
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahi.

श्री नारायण अंग समाहीं॥
Shri Narayan Ang Samahi.

क्षीरसिन्धु में करत विलासा।
Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilasa.

दयासिन्धु दीजै मन आसा॥
Dayasindhu Deejai Man Aasa.

हिंगलाज में तुम्हीं भवानी।
Hinglaj Mein Tumhi Bhavani.

महिमा अमित न जात बखानी॥
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani.

मातंगी अरु धूमावती माता।
Matangi Aru Dhumavati Mata.

भुवनेश्वरी बगलामुखि माता॥
Bhuvaneshwari Baglamukhi Mata.

श्री भैरव तारा जग तारी।
Shri Bhairav Tara Jag Tari.

छिन्न भाल भव दुःख निवारी॥
Chhinn Bhal Bhav Dukh Nivari.

केहरि वाहन सोह भवानी।
Kehr Vahan Soh Bhavani.

लांगुर वीर चलत अगवानी॥
Langur Veer Chalat Agvani.

कर में खप्पर खड्ग विराजै।
Kar Mein Khappar Khadg Virajai.

जाको देख काल डर भाजै॥
Jako Dekh Kaal Dar Bhajai.

सोहै अस्त्र और त्रिशूला।
Sohai Astra Aur Trishula.

जाते उठत शत्रु हिय शूला॥
Jaate Uthat Shatru Hiy Shula.

नागार्जुन को दिया सहाई।
Nagarjun Ko Diya Sahayai.

ताहि जीति बने जगत गुराई॥
Tahi Jeet Bane Jagat Gurai.

शुम्भ निशुम्भ दानव तुम मारे।
Shumbh Nishumbh Danav Tum Maare.

रक्तबीज शंखन संहारे॥
Raktabeej Shankhan Sanhare.

महिषासुर नृप अति अभिमानी।
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani.

जेहि अघ भार मही अकुलानी॥
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulani.

रूप कराल कालिका धारा।
Roop Karal Kalika Dhara.

सेन सहित तुम तिहि संहारा॥
Sen Sahit Tum Tihi Sanhara.

परी गाढ़ संतन पर जब जब।
Pari Gaadh Santan Par Jab Jab.

भई सहाय मातु तुम तब तब॥
Bhayi Sahay Matu Tum Tab Tab.

अमरपुरी अरु बासव लोका।
Amarpuri Aru Basav Loka.

तब महिमा सब रहें अशोका॥
Tab Mahima Sab Rahen Ashoka.

ज्वाला में है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari.

तुमको सदा पूजें नरनारी॥
Tumko Sada Poojen Narnari.

प्रेम भक्ति से जो यश गावे।
Prem Bhakti Se Jo Yash Gave.

दुःख दारिद्र निकट नहिं आवे॥
Dukh Daridr Nikat Nahi Aave.

ध्यावे तुम्हें जो नर मन लाई।
Dhyave Tumhe Jo Nar Man Laai.

जनम मरन ताकौ छुटि जाई॥
Janam Maran Tako Chhuti Jaai.

जोगी सुर मुनि कहत पुकारी।
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukari.

योग न हो बिन शक्ति तुम्हारी॥
Yog Na Ho Bin Shakti Tumhari.

॥ दोहा ॥
शंकर आचारज तप कीनो।
Shankar Aacharya Tap Kino.

काम अरु क्रोध जीति सब लीनो॥
Kaam Aru Krodh Jeet Sab Leeno.

निशिदिन ध्यान धरो शंकर को।
Nishidin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko.

काहु काल नहिं सुमिरो तुमको॥
Kahu Kaal Nahi Sumiro Tumko.

शक्ति रूप का मरम न पायो।
Shakti Roop Ka Maram Na Payo.

शक्ति गई तब मन पछितायो॥
Shakti Gayi Tab Man Pachhitayo.

॥ समापन ॥
शरणागत हुई कीर्ति बखानी।
Sharanagat Hui Kirti Bakhani.

जय जय जय जगदम्ब भवानी॥
Jai Jai Jai Jagdamba Bhavani.

🌸 जय माता दी! 🌸
Jai Mata Di!

snippet.title: फिलहाल चालू है मतलब चल रहा है कब तक चलेगा उसकी कोई गारंटी नहीं है | Vijay Raaz, Asrani | Comedy Clip
snippet.description:
फिलहाल चालू है मतलब चल रहा है कब तक चलेगा उसकी कोई गारंटी नहीं है | Vijay Raaz, Asrani | Comedy Clip

  #dhamaalmovie #jaavedjaaferi #sanjaymishra 

Dhamaal is about four friends afflicted by the get rich quick virus. Their fortunes take a turn after they accidentally bump into a victim who tells them about a hidden treasure who tells them about a hidden treasure in Goa including 10 crore rupees. The group race toward Goa in Contractors stolen car little knowing that their plans will soon be foiled albeit hilariously by Police Inspector Kabir Nayak - Sanjay Dutt.

Movie - Dhamaal
StarCast - Sanjay Dutt, Ritesh Deshmukh, Arshad Warsi, Jaaved Jaaferi, Asrani, Sanjay Mishra, Vijay Raaz, Tiku Talsania, Prem Chopra
Director - Indra Kumar

धमाल चार दोस्तों की कहानी है जो जल्दी अमीर बनो वायरस से पीड़ित हैं। उनकी किस्मत तब बदल जाती है जब वे गलती से एक शिकार से टकरा जाते हैं जो उन्हें एक छिपे हुए खजाने के बारे में बताता है जो उन्हें 10 करोड़ रुपये सहित गोवा में छिपे खजाने के बारे में बताता है। ठेकेदारों की चोरी की कार में गोवा की ओर समूह की दौड़ यह जानते हुए भी कि उनकी योजना जल्द ही पुलिस इंस्पेक्टर कबीर नायक - संजय दत्त द्वारा प्रफुल्लित रूप से विफल कर दी जाएगी।

फिल्म- धमाल
स्टार कास्ट - संजय दत्त, रितेश देशमुख, अरशद वारसी, जावेद जाफ़री, असरानी, ​​संजय मिश्रा, विजय राज, टीकू तलसानिया, प्रेम चोपड़ा

snippet.title: नवरात्रि का तीसरा दिन~माँ चंद्रघंटा की आरती | ॐ जय चंद्रघंटा माता Chandraghanta Aarti,Navratri Day-3
snippet.description:
नवरात्रि का तीसरा दिन~माँ चंद्रघंटा की आरती | ॐ जय चंद्रघंटा माता Chandraghanta Aarti,Navratri Day-3
नवरात्रि का तीसरा दिन~माँ चंद्रघंटा की आरती | ॐ जय चंद्रघंटा माता Chandraghanta Aarti,Navratri Day-3
नवरात्रि का तीसरा दिन~माँ चंद्रघंटा की आरती | ॐ जय चंद्रघंटा माता Chandraghanta Aarti,Navratri Day-3
नवरात्रि का तीसरा दिन~माँ चंद्रघंटा की आरती | ॐ जय चंद्रघंटा माता Chandraghanta Aarti,Navratri Day-3
नवरात्रि का तीसरा दिन~माँ चंद्रघंटा की आरती | ॐ जय चंद्रघंटा माता Chandraghanta Aarti,Navratri Day-3
नवरात्रि का तीसरा दिन~माँ चंद्रघंटा की आरती | ॐ जय चंद्रघंटा माता Chandraghanta Aarti,Navratri Day-3

माँ दुर्गाजी की तीसरी शक्ति का नाम चंद्रघंटा है। नवरात्रि उपासना में तीसरे दिन की पूजा का अत्यधिक महत्व है और इस दिन इन्हीं के विग्रह का पूजन-आराधन किया जाता है। इस दिन साधक का मन 'मणिपूर' चक्र में प्रविष्ट होता है। लोकवेद के अनुसार माँ चंद्रघंटा की कृपा से अलौकिक वस्तुओं के दर्शन होते हैं, दिव्य सुगंधियों का अनुभव होता है तथा विविध प्रकार की दिव्य ध्वनियाँ सुनाई देती हैं। ये क्षण साधक के लिए अत्यंत सावधान रहने के होते हैं।

Credits:
Title:  मां चन्द्रघंटा की आरती | Maa Chandraghanta Aarti
Singer: Anju Sharma
Music Director: Gulshan Music
Edit & Gfx: Vats Media
Music Label: Vats Records
